          <p class="description-text">1) Hackers will create up to 4 person teams ideally with a wide variety of talent.</p>
          <p class="description-text">2) The <i>problem questions</i> for the hackathon will be announced and for the next 24 hours you and your team will attempt to solve one or more of them.</p>
          <p class="description-text">3) At the end of the hacking period, you will get a chance to demo and pitch what you have created and be judged. Prizes for teams that create the best solutions will then be handed out.</p>
